# ruleforge
Explainable rules &amp; decision engine for modern applications

# TaskMind

TaskMind is an intelligent and explainable rules engine with:
- Rule priorities
- Conflict detection
- Human-readable explanations
- Text-based DSL
- REST API (FastAPI)

## Installation
```bash
pip install taskmind

